{"tid":2051661,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國兩黨議員希望盡快通過制裁賣港官員既法案 / 歐盟研擴大外國投資審查阻中國買家併購","createTime":"2020-06-05T03:07:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T03:08:53.000Z","uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"be145ecdd66102a2bf724b1893cf234fc9916499","tid":2051661,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:07:23.000Z","msg":"美國共和黨參議員圖米（Patrick Toomey）說，無論共和黨或民主黨議員，都希望參院盡快通過法案，制裁損害香港自治的中國官員和當地銀行。<br />\n<br />\n圖米在參議院銀行委員會聽證會上說，兩黨議員都希望盡快通過法案。圖米與民主黨參議員范赫倫（Chris Van Hollen）上月聯合提出法案，制裁需對中國在香港強推「港版國安法」負責的個別官員，凍結他們在美國資產。與以往法案不同，與該些官員有相當多交易的中資銀行，也會成為制裁目標，包括切斷它們與美國銀行業的連繫及限制它們進行美元交易。<br />\n<br />\n支聯會主席李卓人亦有透過網絡連線參與聽證會⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200605/IREBMIDWLEB743KJMIQYG3IXEQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200605%2FIREBMIDWLEB743KJMIQYG3IXEQ%2F&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5ErM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=e6e9cbfb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200605%2FIREBMIDWLEB743KJMIQYG3IXEQ%2F&h=d63cc55e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200605/IREBMIDWLEB743KJMIQYG3IXEQ/</a>"},{"pid":"84d97069ec1a6cef91d6c9a610f8624f93ae1a37","tid":2051661,"uid":153151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:07:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Xz0C0n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Xz0C0n.jpg&h=7b7d0741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n誠懇呼籲唔好再舉美國旗，你唔係美國人又搞佢哋支旗，美國人會好反感<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/djateT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/djateT</a><br />\n#1 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0eed408105a080c68379bd827f8d04f16056158c","tid":2051661,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:08:17.000Z","msg":"一份公開文件草案顯示，歐盟執委會提議擴大對區內外國投資的審查範圍，以保護更多行業不被潛在的中國買家收購。倘歐盟各國於6月15日前不提出反對，該草案將獲得通過。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2486967\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2486967&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5ErM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=f4337fdb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2486967</a>"},{"pid":"627acc4e26898ef547c731e3871cccb5fdec7c9c","tid":2051661,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:08:53.000Z","msg":"最緊要搞埋班仆街嘅屋企人"}]}